Membership&#xd;
 &#xd;
	Section 1 :     Definition&#xd;
Anyone who fills out the membership form, pays dues and abides by the membership guidelines of ICSHD is a member.&#xd;
ICSHD  members receive discounts or fee waivers for some of the facilities and activities of the center.&#xd;
 &#xd;
	Section 2 :    Suspension or Termination of Membership&#xd;
If any member fails to fulfill the membership requirements or fails to abide by the membership guidelines of the center, the Board of Directors may suspend or terminate their membership. They may chose not to refund part or any of the membership fees paid by the member at the time of termination, depending on the circumstances&#xd;
&#xd;
All member information is available upon request&#xd;
All member cards are published continuously on the International Commission for Human Development Scientists page&#xd;
